# ─── Whitelist: this repo tracks only the customization toolkit ───────
# Strategy: ignore EVERYTHING, then re-include just the toolkit folders
# and a short list of root files. Anything else — any deck, asset folder,
# script, or new root file, now or in the future — is ignored by default
# and will not be committed.

# Ignore every top-level entry...
/*

# ...re-include the toolkit: the shared core + the look variants...
!/core/
!/variants/

# ...and these root files only.
!/.gitignore
!/package.json
!/pnpm-lock.yaml
!/pnpm-workspace.yaml
!/README.md
!/slides.md
!/Slidev_tutorial.md

# Selected content out of pages/ — re-include the dir (so git descends),
# ignore its contents, then keep just the demo section and the tutorial
# deck's sections. Everything else under pages/ stays ignored.
!/pages/
/pages/*
!/pages/example.md
!/pages/tutorial/

# ...and two demo assets out of public/ (same three-step, then pick the files).
# Everything else under public/ — other decks' images — stays ignored.
!/public/
/public/*
!/public/tutorial/
/public/tutorial/*
!/public/tutorial/layout-demo.svg
!/public/tutorial/slidev-logo.png

# Junk to keep out even inside the tracked folders above.
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.log
